show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A marriage no one remembers, a love neither expected. Two strangers wed for a dying wish, then meet again as boss and employee, unaware they’re already husband and wife. When love returns in disguise, how long can destiny keep its secret?
